sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Svelte)
    participant A as App (Wails Binding)

    Note over C,A: GetLocale [direct OS interaction]
    C->>A: GetLocale()
    A->>A: Check LC_ALL, LANG env vars
    A->>A: Fallback: exec("defaults read NSGlobalDomain AppleLocale")
    A->>A: Fallback: "en-US"
    A-->>C: string (BCP 47 locale tag)

    Note over C,A: LogFrontend [direct slog]
    C->>A: LogFrontend(level, message, source)
    A->>A: slog.Error/Warn/Info(message, source, "frontend")
    A-->>C: void
